<!doctype html>  -->it shows that it is a html document.
<html>  --> it is a starting tag.
</html> --> it is ending tag.
there is two basic sections
1)<head>---</head >  head of the document.
2)<body>...</body>   body of the document.
tags inside the head.
<title>---</title>--- title of the website
meta tag-->it is basically that define information about our file
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="description" content ="this is awesome".

it says that the document has this kind of character set,it is a description for the website.

other tags insiide body
* <p>--</p> paragraph tag.
we can enter the content inside the body.


 
